<item>
            <title>[LU-5597] Kernel Module.symvers take precendene instead of MOFED provided</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5597</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I was able to compile ko2iblnd and other module but all symbol versions were taken from /usr/src/linux-headers-3.13.0-32-generic/Module.symvers instead of /usr/src/mlnx-ofed-kernel-2.3/Module.symvers and as result load of ko2iblnd module fails.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Ubuntu 14.04&lt;br/&gt;
Kernel - 3.13.0-32-generic&lt;br/&gt;
MLNX_OFED_LINUX-2.3-1.0.0</environment>
