                            <comment id="113217" author="simmonsja" created="Thu, 23 Apr 2015 15:19:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Can you try the latest master branch from Intel. The patch from &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5953&quot; title=&quot;lustre[-dkms] needs to automatically account for OFED&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-5953&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-5953&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; should have addressed this issue. BTW I&apos;m running the same setup as you are Aleksey&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
